
# Install Spring Tool Suite / STS

STS is an Eclipse-based development environment used for developing Spring applications.

By using STS, we can develop Java Standard Edition or Spring-based applications or We can also develop Spring-based Web applications.

STS provides functionalities for Spring applications - Develop, Run, Debug and Test

## Download Spring Tools Suite for the developer OS environment

# Go to https://spring.io/tools. Select the desired OS environment. For Windows-OS, select Windows 64-Bit
# Also make sure, you have at least Java SE 8u45 JDK being installed. Not the JRE.
